snippet.title: Aeon Must Die! (Raw alpha gameplay)
snippet.description:
Aeon Must Die! is a genre-fusing hardcore action-rpg coming to PC and consoles.

This trailer features raw gameplay footage from the alpha version of the game and does not represent the quality of the final product. 

The music was composed by Lev Knipper in 1933.

Instagram: Limestone_Games
Twitter: @Limestone_Games
